## 🚧 Challenges Faced

- SSH connection failures  
- Key pair mismatch issues  
- Private key permission errors (Windows)  
- Networking and route table debugging  

---

## 💡 Key Learnings

- Practical understanding of Infrastructure as Code (IaC)  
- Importance of debugging in DevOps  
- Deep understanding of AWS networking  
- Handling real-world SSH and security issues  

---

